revisions.description: Rev 0.1 23 May 2011 00:00 Initial version of the TIMETRA-DA-MIB.

tmnxDASvrGrpTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDASvrGrpTableLastChanged
tmnxDASvrGrpTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDASvrGrpTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDASvrGrpTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDASvrGrpTable.name: tmnxDASvrGrpTable
tmnxDASvrGrpTable.description: There can be multiple Delivery Appliance (DA) proxy server groups in a system. One or more caching blades (DA servers) form a server group. A caching blade can appear in only one server group. The tmnxDASvrGrpTable has an entry for each such server group in the system.

tmnxDASvrGrpEntry.name: tmnxDASvrGrpEntry
tmnxDASvrGrpEntry.description: Each row entry represents a DA server group in the system. Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDASvrGrpIndex.name: tmnxDASvrGrpIndex
tmnxDASvrGrpIndex.description: The value of tmnxDASvrGrpIndex specifies the server group index for this server group.

tmnxDASvrGrpRowStatus.name: tmnxDASvrGrpRowStatus
tmnxDASvrGrpRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDASvrGrpRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the DA Server Group Table. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table.

tmnxDASvrGrpLastChanged.name: tmnxDASvrGrpLastChanged
tmnxDASvrGrpLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDASvrGrpLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDASvrGrpTable.

tmnxDASvrGrpCardSlotNumber.name: tmnxDASvrGrpCardSlotNumber
tmnxDASvrGrpCardSlotNumber.description: The bit value of tmnxDASvrGrpCardSlotNumber specifies the card number being used by the DA server.

tmnxDASvrGrpAdminState.name: tmnxDASvrGrpAdminState
tmnxDASvrGrpAdminState.description: The value of tmnxDASvrGrpAdminState specifies the desired administrative state of the DA server-group.

tmnxDASvrGrpOperState.name: tmnxDASvrGrpOperState
tmnxDASvrGrpOperState.description: The value of tmnxDASvrGrpOperState indicates the current operational state of the DA server-group.

tmnxDAGrpTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDAGrpTableLastChanged
tmnxDAGrpTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDAGrpTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDAGrpTable.name: tmnxDAGrpTable
tmnxDAGrpTable.description: The tmnxDAGrpTable has an entry for each virtual Delivery Appliance (DA) proxy server in a server group. There can be multiple virtual DA proxy servers within a server group.

tmnxDAGrpEntry.name: tmnxDAGrpEntry
tmnxDAGrpEntry.description: Each row entry represents a virtual DA proxy server. Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDAGrpName.name: tmnxDAGrpName
tmnxDAGrpName.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpName specifies the group name for this virtual DA proxy server in the specified server group.

tmnxDAGrpRowStatus.name: tmnxDAGrpRowStatus
tmnxDAGrpRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the DA group table. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table. The value of the object tmnxDAGrpServerGroupIndex specifies the index of the server group on which this DA Group must be instantiated. The value of tmnxDAGrpServerGroupIndex must be specified when the row is created and cannot be changed while tmnxDAGrpRowStatus is 'active'.

tmnxDAGrpLastChanged.name: tmnxDAGrpLastChanged
tmnxDAGrpLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDAGrpTable.

tmnxDAGrpServerGroupIndex.name: tmnxDAGrpServerGroupIndex
tmnxDAGrpServerGroupIndex.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpServerGroupIndex specifies the index of the server group on which this DA Group must be instantiated. The value of this object must be specified when the row is created and cannot be changed while tmnxDAGrpRowStatus is 'active'. An 'inconsistentValue' error is returned if an attempt is made to set this object individually.

tmnxDAGrpAdminState.name: tmnxDAGrpAdminState
tmnxDAGrpAdminState.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpAdminState specifies the desired administrative state of the DA group.

tmnxDAGrpDescription.name: tmnxDAGrpDescription
tmnxDAGrpDescription.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDescription specifies the user provided description string for this DA group entry.

tmnxDAGrpDnsClientIsmLinkName.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsClientIsmLinkName
tmnxDAGrpDnsClientIsmLinkName.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDnsClientIsmLinkName specifies the Integrated Services Module (ISM) link name used in DNS lookup request packets. The ISM link is an IP interface in the DA group on the ISM. The ISM link must already be configured in the DA group before it is assigned to this object.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCache.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCache
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCache.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCache specifies what happens when the DA loses connectivity to all DCs in the network. A value of 'none' specifies that the cache is invalidated and all incoming delivery requests will be rejected. A value of 'useCache' specifies that the DA will continue to use its cached authorizations until they expire.

tmnxDAGrpDCAdminState.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAdminState
tmnxDAGrpDCAdminState.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAdminState specifies the desired administrative state of the DA group for this DC.

tmnxDAGrpDCIsmLinkName.name: tmnxDAGrpDCIsmLinkName
tmnxDAGrpDCIsmLinkName.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCIsmLinkName specifies the Integrated Services Module (ISM) link name used in the DA group for this DC. The ISM link is an IP interface in the DA group on the ISM. The ISM link must already be configured in the DA group before it is assigned to this object.

tmnxDAGrpDCBootStrapPort.name: tmnxDAGrpDCBootStrapPort
tmnxDAGrpDCBootStrapPort.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCBootStrapPort specifies the DC port number of the bootstrap-servers.

tmnxDAGrpDCConnRetryTimer.name: tmnxDAGrpDCConnRetryTimer
tmnxDAGrpDCConnRetryTimer.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCConnRetryTimer specifies in milli-seconds the amount of time after which the delivery-controller will retry periodically to establish a connection with its client if not initially successful.

tmnxDAGrpDCIdleTimeout.name: tmnxDAGrpDCIdleTimeout
tmnxDAGrpDCIdleTimeout.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCIdleTimeout specifies the max time for any outstanding requests to a delivery-controller to be replied. If a reply is not received within this time after the request was sent, the DA closes the TCP connection.

tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCache.name: tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCache
tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCache.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCache indicates the number of bytes that are served from the cache.

tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheL32.name: tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheL32
tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheH32.name: tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheH32
tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCacheH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpBytesFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCache.name: tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCache
tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCache.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCache indicates the number of bytes that are fetched from the server and not served from the cache.

tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheL32.name: tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheL32
tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheH32.name: tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheH32
tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCacheH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpBytesNotFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCache.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCache
tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCache.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCache indicates the number of objects that are served from the cache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheL32.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheL32
tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheH32.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheH32
tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCacheH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCache.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCache
tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCache.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCache indicates the number of objects that are fetched from the server and not served from the cache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheL32.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheL32
tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheH32.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheH32
tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCacheH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpObjectsNotFromCache.

tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCount.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCount
tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCount.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCount indicates object byte count.

tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountL32.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountL32
tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCount.

tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountH32.name: tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountH32
tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCountH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpObjectByteCount.

tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOrigins.name: tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOrigins
tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOrigins.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOrigins indicates the number of origin servers.

tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsL32.name: tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsL32
tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOrigins.

tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsH32.name: tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsH32
tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOriginsH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpNumberOfOrigins.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHit.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHit
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHit.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHit indicates the number of auth cache hits.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitL32.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitL32
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHit.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitH32.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitH32
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHitH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheHit.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMiss.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMiss
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMiss.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMiss indicates the number of auth cache misses.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissL32.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissL32
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMiss.

tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissH32.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissH32
tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMissH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpDCAuthCacheMiss.

tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuth.name: tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuth
tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuth.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuth indicates the number of denied auth sessions.

tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthL32.name: tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthL32
tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthL32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuth.

tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthH32.name: tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthH32
tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthH32.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuthH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAGrpDCDeniedAuth.

tmnxDAGrpDCMinRTTPerPeer.name: tmnxDAGrpDCMinRTTPerPeer
tmnxDAGrpDCMinRTTPerPeer.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCMinRTTPerPeer indicates the minimum Round Trip Time per peer.

tmnxDAGrpDCAvgRTTPerPeer.name: tmnxDAGrpDCAvgRTTPerPeer
tmnxDAGrpDCAvgRTTPerPeer.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCAvgRTTPerPeer indicates the average Round Trip Time per peer.

tmnxDAGrpDCMaxRTTPerPeer.name: tmnxDAGrpDCMaxRTTPerPeer
tmnxDAGrpDCMaxRTTPerPeer.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDCMaxRTTPerPeer indicates the maximum Round Trip Time per peer.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTableLastChanged
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable.description: The tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable has an entry for each DNS server IP address within a Delivery Appliance (DA) group network. A user can provision up to four DNS server IP addresses per DA group.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrEntry.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrEntry
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrEntry.description: Each row entry represents a DNS server IP address within a DA group network. Entries can be created and deleted by the user. A maximum of four entries can be configured.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddrTyp.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddrTyp
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddrTyp.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddrTyp specifies the address-type of the DNS server IP address.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddress.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddress
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddress.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrAddress specifies the IP address of a DNS server in a DA group.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrRowStatus.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrRowStatus
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table.

tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrLastChanged.name: tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrLastChanged
tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDAGrpDnsSvrTable.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrTableLastChanged
tmnxDADCBtStSvrTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable
tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable.description: The tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable has an entry for each Delivery Controller (DC) bootstrap server. The bootstrap server is used at Delivery Appliance (DA) initialization. The DA downloads the rest of the DC list from one of the bootstrap servers. Multiple bootstrap servers can be specified per DA Group for redundancy purposes.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrEntry.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrEntry
tmnxDADCBtStSvrEntry.description: Each row entry represents a DC bootstrap server. Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrIndex.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrIndex
tmnxDADCBtStSvrIndex.description: The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrIndex specifies a unique value which identifies this bootstrap server entry.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrRowStatus.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrRowStatus
tmnxDADCBtStSvrRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table. The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddrType and tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddress must also be specified when the row is created.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrLastChanged.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrLastChanged
tmnxDADCBtStSvrLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDADCBtStSvrTable.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddrType.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddrType
tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddrType.description: The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddrType specifies the type of address represented by tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddress.

tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddress.name: tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddress
tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddress.description: The value of tmnxDADCBtStSvrAddress specifies the IP Address or DNS name of the bootstrap server. If the IP address is an IPv4 address, it must be specified in the a.b.c.d dotted-decimal notation. An IPv6 address must be specified as defined in RFC1924.

tmnxDAHttpTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDAHttpTableLastChanged
tmnxDAHttpTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDAHttpTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDAHttpTable.name: tmnxDAHttpTable
tmnxDAHttpTable.description: The tmnxDAHttpTable has an entry for each Delivery Appliance (DA) group. Each row entry specifies the HTTP proxy configuration for this DA group.

tmnxDAHttpEntry.name: tmnxDAHttpEntry
tmnxDAHttpEntry.description: Each row entry represents the HTTP proxy configuration for a DA group. Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDAHttpLastChanged.name: tmnxDAHttpLastChanged
tmnxDAHttpLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDAHttpTable.

tmnxDAHttpServerAdminState.name: tmnxDAHttpServerAdminState
tmnxDAHttpServerAdminState.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerAdminState specifies the desired administrative state of the HTTP server's configuration for this DA group.

tmnxDAHttpServerOperState.name: tmnxDAHttpServerOperState
tmnxDAHttpServerOperState.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerOperState indicates the current operational state of the HTTP server's configuration for this DA group.

tmnxDAHttpServerIdleTimeout.name: tmnxDAHttpServerIdleTimeout
tmnxDAHttpServerIdleTimeout.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerIdleTimeout specifies the time interval after which the http-server will timeout and close the HTTP connection if there has been no activity on that connection for that time.

tmnxDAHttpServerViaString.name: tmnxDAHttpServerViaString
tmnxDAHttpServerViaString.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerViaString specifies the HTTP via header.

tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUse.name: tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUse
tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUse.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUse indicates the amount of bandwidth that is used by the HTTP server while streaming content. This object follows the behavior of a gauge64 in that its value can increase or decrease with time.

tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseL32
tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUse.

tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseH32
tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUseH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServerStrBWInUse.

tmnxDAHttpServerXferInProg.name: tmnxDAHttpServerXferInProg
tmnxDAHttpServerXferInProg.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferInProg indicates the number of HTTP transfers that are in progress by the HTTP server.

tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompleted.name: tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompleted
tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompleted.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompleted indicates the number of HTTP transfers that have been completed by the HTTP server.

tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedL32
tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompleted.

tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedH32
tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompletedH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferCompleted.

tmnxDAHttpServerXferTimeouts.name: tmnxDAHttpServerXferTimeouts
tmnxDAHttpServerXferTimeouts.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferTimeouts indicates the number of HTTP server sessions that timed out due to inactivity.

tmnxDAHttpServerXferFailed.name: tmnxDAHttpServerXferFailed
tmnxDAHttpServerXferFailed.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerXferFailed indicates the number of HTTP transfers that failed when the HTTP server was transferring HTTP content.

tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequests.name: tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequests
tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequests.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequests indicates the number of valid HTTP requests that were received by the HTTP server.

tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsL32
tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequests.

tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsH32
tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequestsH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServerValidRequests.

tmnxDAHttpServerInvalidRequests.name: tmnxDAHttpServerInvalidRequests
tmnxDAHttpServerInvalidRequests.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerInvalidRequests indicates the number of invalid HTTP requests that were received by the HTTP server.

tmnxDAHttpServerMethodNotSuppted.name: tmnxDAHttpServerMethodNotSuppted
tmnxDAHttpServerMethodNotSuppted.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerMethodNotSuppted indicates the number of times the HTTP server rejected the request because the requested method is not supported.

tmnxDAHttpServerHostNotSuppted.name: tmnxDAHttpServerHostNotSuppted
tmnxDAHttpServerHostNotSuppted.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServerHostNotSuppted indicates the number of times the HTTP server rejected the request because the requested host is not supported.

tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSent.name: tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSent
tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSent.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSent indicates the count of type 1XX error responses sent by the HTTP Server.

tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentL32
tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentH32
tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSentH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer1XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSent.name: tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSent
tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSent.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSent indicates the count of type 2XX error responses sent by the HTTP Server.

tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentL32
tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentH32
tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSentH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer2XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSent.name: tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSent
tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSent.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSent indicates the count of type 3XX error responses sent by the HTTP Server.

tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentL32
tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentH32
tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSentH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer3XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSent.name: tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSent
tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSent.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSent indicates the count of type 4XX error responses sent by the HTTP Server.

tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentL32
tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentH32
tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSentH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer4XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSent.name: tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSent
tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSent.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSent indicates the count of type 5XX error responses sent by the HTTP Server.

tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentL32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentL32
tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentH32.name: tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentH32
tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSentH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpServer5XXCountSent.

tmnxDAHttpIngestAdminState.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestAdminState
tmnxDAHttpIngestAdminState.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestAdminState specifies the desired administrative state of the HTTP proxy's ingest configuration for this DA group.

tmnxDAHttpIngestOperState.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestOperState
tmnxDAHttpIngestOperState.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestOperState indicates the current operational state of the HTTP proxy's ingest configuration for this DA group.

tmnxDAHttpIngestIsmLinkName.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestIsmLinkName
tmnxDAHttpIngestIsmLinkName.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestIsmLinkName specifies the Integrated Services Module (ISM) link name used for HTTP ingest connections to the origin server. The ISM link is an IP interface in the DA group on the ISM. The ISM link must already be configured in the DA group before it is assigned to this object.

tmnxDAHttpIngestIdleTimeout.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestIdleTimeout
tmnxDAHttpIngestIdleTimeout.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestIdleTimeout specifies the time interval after which the HTTP proxy will timeout and close the HTTP connection if there has been no activity from the origin server on that connection for that time.

tmnxDAHttpIngestXferInProg.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestXferInProg
tmnxDAHttpIngestXferInProg.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferInProg indicates the number of HTTP ingest transfers in progress from the origin server to the HTTP proxy.

tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompleted.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompleted
tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompleted.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompleted indicates the number of HTTP ingest transfers completed from the origin server to the HTTP proxy.

tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedL32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedL32
tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompleted.

tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedH32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedH32
tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompletedH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferCompleted.

tmnxDAHttpIngestXferTimeouts.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestXferTimeouts
tmnxDAHttpIngestXferTimeouts.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferTimeouts indicates the number of HTTP ingest transfers from the origin server to the HTTP proxy that timed-out.

tmnxDAHttpIngestXferFailed.name: tmnxDAHttpIngestXferFailed
tmnxDAHttpIngestXferFailed.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngestXferFailed indicates the number of HTTP ingest transfers that failed from the origin server to the HTTP proxy.

tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecd.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecd
tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecd.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecd indicates the count of type 1XX errors that were received by the HTTP proxy from the origin server.

tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdL32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdL32
tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdH32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdH32
tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecdH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest1XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecd.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecd
tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecd.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecd indicates the count of type 2XX errors that were received by the HTTP proxy from the origin server.

tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdL32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdL32
tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdH32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdH32
tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecdH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest2XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecd.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecd
tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecd.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecd indicates the count of type 3XX errors that were received by the HTTP proxy from the origin server.

tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdL32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdL32
tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdH32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdH32
tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecdH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest3XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecd.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecd
tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecd.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecd indicates the count of type 4XX errors that were received by the HTTP proxy from the origin server.

tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdL32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdL32
tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdH32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdH32
tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecdH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest4XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecd.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecd
tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecd.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecd indicates the count of type 5XX errors that were received by the HTTP proxy from the origin server.

tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdL32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdL32
tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdL32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdH32.name: tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdH32
tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdH32.description: The value of tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecdH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDAHttpIngest5XXCountRecd.

tmnxDAIsmLinkTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkTableLastChanged
tmnxDAIsmLinkTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDAIsmLinkTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDAIsmLinkTable.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkTable
tmnxDAIsmLinkTable.description: The tmnxDAIsmLinkTable has an entry for each ISM-link within a group configured in the Delivery Appliance (DA). Multiple IP ISM-links in the same group are assumed to belong to the same network. IP ISM-links in different groups are currently assumed to belong to different networks.

tmnxDAIsmLinkEntry.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkEntry
tmnxDAIsmLinkEntry.description: Each row entry represents an Integrated Services Module (ISM) link within a group configured in the Delivery Appliance (DA). Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDAIsmLinkName.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkName
tmnxDAIsmLinkName.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkName specifies the ISM-link name within a group in the DA.

tmnxDAIsmLinkRowStatus.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkRowStatus
tmnxDAIsmLinkRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the tmnxDAIsmLinkTable. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table.

tmnxDAIsmLinkLastChanged.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkLastChanged
tmnxDAIsmLinkLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDAIsmLinkTable.

tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrType.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrType
tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrType.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrType specifies the address-type of the ISM-link address used in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkAddress.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkAddress
tmnxDAIsmLinkAddress.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkAddress specifies the IP address used for the ISM-link address in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrPrefixLength.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrPrefixLength
tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrPrefixLength.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkAddrPrefixLength specifies the prefix length of the ISM-link address used in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkDescription.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkDescription
tmnxDAIsmLinkDescription.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkDescription specifies the user provided description string for this ISM-link within the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpd.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpd
tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpd.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpd specifies if the HTTP server should be enabled on this ISM-link.

tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpListenPort.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpListenPort
tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpListenPort.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkHttpListenPort specifies the HTTP listner port number on this ISM-link if HTTPD is enabled on this ISM-link.

tmnxDAIsmLinkIpMtu.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkIpMtu
tmnxDAIsmLinkIpMtu.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkIpMtu specifies the Maximum Transmission Unit (MTU) value for this ISM-link within the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkQtag.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkQtag
tmnxDAIsmLinkQtag.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkQtag specifies the ISM-link identifier for this ISM-link within the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkMacAddress.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkMacAddress
tmnxDAIsmLinkMacAddress.description: The value of the object tmnxDAIsmLinkMacAddress specifies the MAC address for this ISM-link within the DA group. By default the system will use an internally generated MAC address.

tmnxDAIsmLinkAdminState.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkAdminState
tmnxDAIsmLinkAdminState.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkAdminState specifies the desired administrative state of the ISM-link used in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkOperState.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkOperState
tmnxDAIsmLinkOperState.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkOperState indicates the current operational state of the ISM-link used in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkBindings.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkBindings
tmnxDAIsmLinkBindings.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkBindings indicates whether the ism-link is configured on the delivery-controller, http-ingest and dns-client. If the bit for an entity is set, it indicates that the ism-link has been configured on that entity. If the bit for an entity is unset it indicates that the ism-link is not configured on the entity.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTableLastChanged
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable.description: The tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable has an entry for each ARP address of an interface within a Delivery Appliance (DA) group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpEntry.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpEntry
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpEntry.description: Each row entry represents an ARP address of an interface within a DA group. Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddrType.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddrType
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddrType.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddrType specifies the ARP address-type of the interface used in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddress.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddress
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddress.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkArpAddress specifies the ARP address of the interface used in the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpRowStatus.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpRowStatus
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkArpRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpLastChanged.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpLastChanged
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAIsmLinkArpLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDAIsmLinkArpTable.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpMacAddr.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpMacAddr
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpMacAddr.description: The value of the object tmnxDAIsmLinkArpMacAddr specifies the MAC address for this ARP interface within the DA group.

tmnxDAIsmLinkArpType.name: tmnxDAIsmLinkArpType
tmnxDAIsmLinkArpType.description: The value of the object tmnxDAIsmLinkArpType indicates if the ARP entry is static or dynamic. When the value of tmnxDAIsmLinkArpType is 'true' the ARP entry is dynamic and when it is 'false' the ARP entry is static.

tmnxDAStRouteTableLastChanged.name: tmnxDAStRouteTableLastChanged
tmnxDAStRouteTableLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteTableLastChanged indicates the sysUpTime at the time of the last modification to tmnxDAStRouteTable by adding, deleting an entry or change to a writable object in the table. If no changes were made to the table since the last re-initialization of the local network management subsystem, then this object contains a zero value.

tmnxDAStRouteTable.name: tmnxDAStRouteTable
tmnxDAStRouteTable.description: The tmnxDAStRouteTable has an entry for each static-route address of an interface within a Delivery Appliance (DA) group.

tmnxDAStRouteEntry.name: tmnxDAStRouteEntry
tmnxDAStRouteEntry.description: Each row entry represents a static-route address of an interface within a DA group. Entries can be created and deleted by the user.

tmnxDAStRouteAddrType.name: tmnxDAStRouteAddrType
tmnxDAStRouteAddrType.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteAddrType specifies the static-route address-type for a static-route the user wishes to create.

tmnxDAStRouteAddress.name: tmnxDAStRouteAddress
tmnxDAStRouteAddress.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteAddress specifies the route address for which the user wishes to create a static-route.

tmnxDAStRoutePrefixLength.name: tmnxDAStRoutePrefixLength
tmnxDAStRoutePrefixLength.description: The value of tmnxDAStRoutePrefixLength specifies the prefix length of the static-route address.

tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddrType.name: tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddrType
tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddrType.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddrType specifies the next-hop address-type for the static-route.

tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddress.name: tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddress
tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddress.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteNextHopAddress specifies the next-hop address for the specified static-route.

tmnxDAStRouteRowStatus.name: tmnxDAStRouteRowStatus
tmnxDAStRouteRowStatus.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteRowStatus specifies the row status of this row in the tmnxDAStRouteTable. It is used to create and delete row entries in this table.

tmnxDAStRouteLastChanged.name: tmnxDAStRouteLastChanged
tmnxDAStRouteLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteLastChanged indicates the timestamp of last change to this row in tmnxDAStRouteTable.

tmnxDAStRouteMetric.name: tmnxDAStRouteMetric
tmnxDAStRouteMetric.description: The value of tmnxDAStRouteMetric specifies the route metric of the static-route.

tmnxDASGCardTable.name: tmnxDASGCardTable
tmnxDASGCardTable.description: There can be multiple Delivery Appliance (DA) proxy server groups in a system. One or more caching blades (DA servers) form a server group. A card can be part of multiple server groups. The tmnxDASGCardTable has an entry for a card in every server group that it is associated with in the system.

tmnxDASGCardEntry.name: tmnxDASGCardEntry
tmnxDASGCardEntry.description: Each row entry represents a DA server-group card entry in the system.

tmnxDASGCardNumber.name: tmnxDASGCardNumber
tmnxDASGCardNumber.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardNumber specifies the card number that is associated with the DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardUpTime.name: tmnxDASGCardUpTime
tmnxDASGCardUpTime.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardUpTime indicates the uptime of the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTotNumTCPConn.name: tmnxDASGCardTotNumTCPConn
tmnxDASGCardTotNumTCPConn.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTotNumTCPConn indicates the total number of TCP connections for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstab.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstab
tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstab.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstab indicates the number of TCP connections that have been established for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabL32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabL32
tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstab.

tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabH32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabH32
tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstabH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnEstab.

tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosed.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosed
tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosed.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosed indicates the number of TCP connections that have been closed for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedL32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedL32
tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosed.

tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedH32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedH32
tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosedH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPConnClosed.

tmnxDASGCardTCPRetries.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPRetries
tmnxDASGCardTCPRetries.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPRetries indicates the number of TCP retries that have been made for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesL32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesL32
tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPRetries.

tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesH32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesH32
tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPRetriesH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPRetries.

tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOut.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOut
tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOut.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOut indicates the number of TCP acknowledgement timeouts that have occured for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutL32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutL32
tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOut.

tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutH32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutH32
tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOutH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPAckTimeOut.

tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosed.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosed
tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosed.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosed indicates the number of TCP connections that have been closed at the receiving end for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedL32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedL32
tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosed.

tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedH32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedH32
tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosedH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPFarEndClosed.

tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosed.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosed
tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosed.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosed indicates the number of TCP connections that have been closed locally for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedL32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedL32
tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosed.

tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedH32.name: tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedH32
tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosedH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardTCPLocalEndClosed.

tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpcty.name: tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpcty
tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpcty.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpcty indicates the amount of used storage capacity for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyL32.name: tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyL32
tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpcty.

tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyH32.name: tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyH32
tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpctyH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardUsedStorageCpcty.

tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpcty.name: tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpcty
tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpcty.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpcty indicates the amount of remaining storage capacity that can be used for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyL32.name: tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyL32
tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyL32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyL32 indicates the lower 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpcty.

tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyH32.name: tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyH32
tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyH32.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpctyH32 indicates the higher 32 bits of the value of tmnxDASGCardRemStorageCpcty.

tmnxDASGCardNumberOfAssets.name: tmnxDASGCardNumberOfAssets
tmnxDASGCardNumberOfAssets.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardNumberOfAssets indicates the number of assets for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardNumberOfOrigins.name: tmnxDASGCardNumberOfOrigins
tmnxDASGCardNumberOfOrigins.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardNumberOfOrigins indicates the number of origin servers connected to this card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardNumberOfURIs.name: tmnxDASGCardNumberOfURIs
tmnxDASGCardNumberOfURIs.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardNumberOfURIs indicates the number of URI's that are connected to this card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardECCBlockCorrections.name: tmnxDASGCardECCBlockCorrections
tmnxDASGCardECCBlockCorrections.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardECCBlockCorrections indicates the number of ECC block corrections for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardECCBlockFailures.name: tmnxDASGCardECCBlockFailures
tmnxDASGCardECCBlockFailures.description: The value of tmnxDASGCardECCBlockFailures indicates the number of ECC block failures for the card within this DA server-group.

tmnxDASGCardPercentBadBlocks.name: tmnxDASGCardPercentBadBlocks
